      <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-stone-800 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span aria-hidden="true">ü•°</span>
        Order-out history
      </h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-stone-500 mb-4">Full record of ordering-in behavior for the nutritionist to review.</p>
